entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_100002_SCRIPT:
Please wait for us princess!
We will not give up on you...
We shall save you no matter
what!!
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_100003_SCRIPT:
To think you would set me free.
Human folly knows no bounds.
No more playing around. Suffer
the full wrath of the gods!,12@202,thum_navi_chara35_2.png,I have nothing to fear now.
As long as I am with my friends
here upon life nor death matters.
We will not lose to you Cardes!

Paris.
Do you think you can beat me?
You know my real power, don't you?
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_70002_SCRIPT:
I'll never forgive you.
Die, you rotten noble!
Your tainted blood is a curse!
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_70003_SCRIPT:

entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_800002_SCRIPT: My time has come to an end. Please forgive me…,

I won't accept I've lost!

I haven't lost yet!!

I've weakened this one enough.

entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_80008_SCRIPT:
I finally get to fight myself,
so don't lose too fast.
Lemme enjoy this a bit.
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_80009_SCRIPT:
You're gonna knock me out?
I didn't know you made jokes.
Sounds too real though, so I can't laugh!
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_80010_SCRIPT:
Don't get cocky...human!!
You should kneel before me
and witness my true power!!
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_80011_SCRIPT:
I'm just getting started myself.
You won't escape this time.
I'm tired of your monkey see, monkey do!
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_80012_SCRIPT:
Karl!
Today I'll finally prove
that I'm way stronger than you!!
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_80013_SCRIPT:
Looks like I can't stop you.
I'll use all I've got then.
Can't take it easy on you and expect to win.
entries.MST_GRANDMISSION_EVENT_90002_SCRIPT:

Knowing it is futile you still
fight? Humans are fools indeed.,12@202,thum_navi_chara35_2.png,We will not lose to you!
